1. *Odabrao* sam ovaj film jer mi se sviđa glumac. (I chose this movie because I like the actor.)
2. Oni su *odabrali* najbolje studente za stipendiju. (They selected the best students for the scholarship.)
3. Kada *odabereš* haljinu, javi mi da li ti je dobra. (When you choose the dress, let me know if it's good for you.)
4. Prošle godine smo *odabrali* ovaj restoran za rođendan. (Last year we picked this restaurant for the birthday party.)
5. *Odabrao bih* tebe da budeš moj timski partner. (I would choose you to be my team partner.)
6. Kako si mogao *odabrati* ovaj auto? Toliko je star! (How could you choose this car? It's so old!)
7. Njihov menadžer je *odabrao* najbolju strategiju za novu kampanju. (Their manager selected the best strategy for the new campaign.)
8. Kada se *odlučiš* koje fakultete želiš da upišeš, javi mi. (When you decide which colleges you want to apply to, let me know.)
9. *Odaberite* željenu veličinu i boju majice. (Choose the desired size and color of the shirt.)
10. Svakog dana moraš *odabrati* između odlaska u teretanu i gledanja televizije. (Every day you have to choose between going to the gym and watching TV.)